      <entry xml:id="entry_rūd" xml:lang="os" abv:completeness="russian-questions">
        <form type="lemma" xml:lang="os-x-iron"><orth>rūd</orth></form>
        <form xml:lang="os-x-digor" type="dialectal"><orth>rod</orth></form>
        <sense><sense><abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
              <q>толстая кишка</q>
            </abv:tr></sense><sense><abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
              <q>колбаса</q>
            </abv:tr></sense></sense>
        <note type="comment">; ср. <ref type="xr" target="#entry_tʼang"/>, <ref type="xr"
            target="#entry_xæloræ" xml:lang="os-x-digor"><lang/>
            <w>xæloræ</w>
            <gloss><q>кишка</q></gloss></ref></note>
        <re>
          <form type="lemma"><orth>ruddag</orth></form>
          <sense><tr xmlns="http://ossetic-studies.org/ns/abaevdict" xml:lang="ru">
              <q xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">нарубленное мясо для колбасы</q>
            </tr></sense>
        </re>
        <exampleGrp xmlns="http://ossetic-studies.org/ns/abaevdict">
          <example>
            <quote xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">æmbīsondy xorz fyn fedtam dyson: Mysyrbijy
              fyny argævstam, axæm <oRef>rūd</oRef> ʒy afældæxtam — ærtæ ivazny</quote>
            <tr xml:lang="ru">
              <q xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">на удивление хороший сон мы видели ночью: мы во
                сне зарезали Мысырби, такую колбасу из него вывернули — три сажени</q>
            </tr>
            <bibl xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0"><ref type="bibl" target="#src_ОЭ"/>
              <biblScope>I 66</biblScope></bibl>
          </example>
          <example>
            <quote xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">gal kæj wydī, ūj ʒy <oRef>rūdy</oRef> xaj dær
              nal fæcī</quote>
            <tr xml:lang="ru">
              <q xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">кому принадлежал бык, тому не досталось даже
                кусочка кишки</q>
            </tr>
            <bibl xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0"><ref type="bibl" target="#src_Ӕмб."/>
              <biblScope>11</biblScope></bibl>
          </example>
        </exampleGrp>
        <etym xml:lang="ru">Восходит к <mentioned xml:lang="ira"><lang/>
            <w type="rec">rauta-</w></mentioned>: <mentioned><mentioned xml:lang="fa"><lang/>
              <w>rūda</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="pal"><lang/>
              <w>rōt</w>, <w>rōtik</w></mentioned>
            <gloss><q>потроха</q></gloss>, <gloss><q>кишки</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned
            xml:lang="ira"><?oxy_comment_start author="Irene" timestamp="20220404T190353+0300" comment="габри"?><lang/><?oxy_comment_end?>
            <w>rutow</w>
            <gloss><q>толстые кишки</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="x-balochi"><lang/>
            <w>rōϑ</w>, <w>rōt</w>, <w>rōtink</w>
            <gloss><q>кишки</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned><mentioned xml:lang="ku"><lang/>
              <w>ruwī</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="ydg"><lang/>
              <w>rūī</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="srh"><lang/>
              <w>raud</w>, <w>rεwd</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="x-rushani"><lang/>
              <w>rūd</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="yah"><lang/>
              <w>rəd</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="isk"><lang/>
              <w>röčik</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="yai"><lang/>
              <w>ruta</w>
              <note type="bibl">(<bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#ref_Андреев._Ягн."/>
                  <biblScope>316</biblScope></bibl>)</note></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="sog"><lang/>
              <w type="rec">rūf-</w>
              <note type="comment">(<w>rwβ-</w>)</note></mentioned><gloss><q>брюхо</q></gloss>,
                <gloss><q>кишки</q></gloss></mentioned> (<bibl><ref type="bibl"
              target="#ref_Henning._BBB"/>
            <biblScope>134</biblScope></bibl>),<note type="footnote"><mentioned xml:lang="sog"
                ><lang>Согд.</lang>
              <w type="rec">rūf-</w></mentioned> из
              <?oxy_comment_start author="Irene" timestamp="20220404T191937+0300" comment="mentioned? иран?"?><w>ruϑwan-</w><?oxy_comment_end?>?
            (ср. <mentioned xml:lang="ae"><lang/>
              <w>uruϑwan-</w>
              <gloss><q>брюхо</q></gloss>, <gloss><q>кишки</q></gloss></mentioned>); <c>ϑw</c> →
              <c>f</c>, как в согдийском манихейском энклит. местоимение 2-го лица ед. ч. <c>-f</c>
            из
              <?oxy_comment_start author="Irene" timestamp="20220404T192152+0300" comment="не понимаю какие mentioned надо делать"?><w>ϑwa</w><?oxy_comment_end?>
                (<bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#ref_Gershevitch"/>
              <biblScope>§ 297</biblScope></bibl>).</note>
          <mentioned><mentioned xml:lang="kho"><lang/>
              <w>rruta-</w>, <w>rrūva-</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="ae"><lang/>
              <w>uruϑwan-</w>, <w>uruϑwar-</w></mentioned>
            <gloss><q>кишки</q></gloss></mentioned>. За пределами иранского мира привлекают
              <mentioned><mentioned xml:lang="sv"><?oxy_comment_start author="Irene" timestamp="20220404T190637+0300" comment="швед. (диал.)"?><lang/><?oxy_comment_end?>
              <w>rudda</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="ang"><lang/>
              <w>rēada</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="en"><lang/>
              <w>read</w></mentioned>
            <gloss><q>сычуг</q></gloss></mentioned>. — Из иранского (аланского или персидского) идут
              <mentioned><mentioned xml:lang="dar"><lang/>
              <w>rud</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="rut"><lang/>
              <w>rud</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="agx"><lang/>
              <w>rud</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="tab"><lang/>
              <w>rad</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="lez"><lang/>
              <w>rad</w></mentioned>
            <gloss><q>кишка</q></gloss></mentioned>. — <bibl><author>Wikander</author>
              (<title>Vayu</title>. <pubPlace>Uppsala—Leipzig</pubPlace>, <date>1941</date>,
              <biblScope>стр. 56–57</biblScope>)</bibl> полагает, что созвучие в <mentioned
            xml:lang="ira"><lang/>
            <w type="rec">rauta-</w><gloss><q>кишки</q></gloss>
            <note type="comment">(<mentioned xml:lang="fa"><lang/>
                <w>rūda</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="pal"><lang/>
                <w>rōt</w></mentioned>)</note></mentioned> и <mentioned xml:lang="ira"><w type="rec"
              >rauta-</w><gloss><q>река</q></gloss>
            <note type="comment">(<mentioned xml:lang="fa"><lang/>
                <w>rōd</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="pal"><lang/>
                <w>rōt</w></mentioned>)</note></mentioned> не случайно; связующим является <q
            rendition="#rend_doublequotes">представление о чем-то, текущем извилинами</q>. В
          качестве семантической параллели <bibl><author>Wikander</author></bibl> приводит
            <mentioned xml:lang="inc-x-old"><lang/>
            <w>guda-</w>
            <gloss><q>кишки</q></gloss></mentioned> — <mentioned xml:lang="ae"><lang/>
            <w>Guδa-</w>
            <gloss>название реки</gloss></mentioned>. Приняв эти соображения, мы приходим к
            <mentioned xml:lang="inc-x-old"><lang/>
            <w>srav-</w>: <w>sruta-</w>
            <gloss><q>течь</q></gloss></mentioned>.<lb/><bibl><author>Stackelberg</author>, <ref
              type="bibl" target="#ref_MSt."/>
            <biblScope>83</biblScope></bibl>. — <bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#ref_Bailey._KhT"/>
            <biblScope>VI 310</biblScope></bibl>; <bibl><title>Studi linguistici in onore di Vittore
              Pisani</title>. <pubPlace>Brescia</pubPlace>, <date>1970</date>, <biblScope>стр.
              92</biblScope></bibl> .</etym>
      </entry>
